com.bmd.android.collection.entry

Interface SparseBooleanArrayEntry

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IntSparseBooleanEntry, IntSparseEntry, SparseBooleanEntry, SparseEntry

    public interface SparseBooleanArrayEntry
extends IntSparseBooleanEntry
    This interface defines a SparseEntry associated with a SparseBooleanArray collection.

    Created by davide on 3/10/14.
